$ON_WWRKCRN
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_WWRKCRN From W1ENTSAL4
Return

$AV_WWRKCRN
If !GWEBSERV
 ## Action FMTCRTPAY
 Call FMTCRTPAY([M]WRKCRY) From TRTDIV
Endif
If !GWEBSERV
 ## Action ASAICRT
 If [F:TCY]CRTFMTFLG<>2 : Grizo =zoncou : mkstat = 1 : Else : Actzo =zoncou : Endif
Endif
Gosub _AFF
Return

